{"name": "quart-auth", "metadata": {"name": "quart-auth", "version": "0.11.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Environment :: Web Environment", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP :: Dynamic Content", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["quart"], "summary": "A Quart extension to provide secure cookie authentication", "upload_time": 1735249664}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  Build Status: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/pgjones/quart-auth/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg\n    :target: https://github.com/pgjones/quart-auth/commits/main\n    ```\n  docs: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/docs-passing-brightgreen.svg\n    :target: https://quart-auth.readthedocs.io\n    ```\n  license: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg\n    :target: https://github.com/pgjones/quart-auth/blob/main/LICENSE\n    ```\n  pypi: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/quart-auth.svg\n    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Quart-Auth/\n    ```\n  python: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/quart-auth.svg\n    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Quart-Auth/\n    ```\n---\n\n# Quart-Auth\n\n{{ Build Status }} {{ docs }} {{ pypi }} {{ python }} {{ license }}\n\nQuart-Auth is an extension for [Quart](https://gitlab.com/pgjones/quart) to provide for secure cookie\nauthentication (session management). It allows for a session to be\nlogged in, authenticated and logged out.\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use Quart-Auth with a Quart app you have to create an QuartAuth and\ninitialise it with the application,\n\n```python\napp = Quart(__name__)\nQuartAuth(app)\n```\n\nor via the factory pattern,\n\n```python\nauth_manager = QuartAuth()\n\ndef create_app():\n    app = Quart(__name__)\n    auth_manager.init_app(app)\n    return app\n```\n\nIn addition you will need to configure Quart-Auth, which defaults to\nthe most secure. At a minimum you will need to set secret key,\n\n```python\napp.secret_key = \"secret key\"  # Do not use this key\n```\n\nwhich you can generate via,\n\n```python\n>>> import secrets\n>>> secrets.token_urlsafe(16)\n```\n\nYou may also need to disable secure cookies to use in development, see\nconfiguration below.\n\nWith QuartAuth initialised you can use the `login_required`\nfunction to decorate routes that should only be accessed by\nauthenticated users,\n\n```python\nfrom quart_auth import login_required\n\n@app.route(\"/\")\n@login_required\nasync def restricted_route():\n    ...\n```\n\nIf no user is logged in, an `Unauthorized` exception is raised. To catch it,\ninstall an error handler,\n\n```python\n@app.errorhandler(Unauthorized)\nasync def redirect_to_login(*_: Exception) -> ResponseReturnValue:\n    return redirect(url_for(\"login\"))\n```\n\nYou can also use the `login_user`, and `logout_user` functions to\nstart and end sessions for a specific `AuthenticatedUser` instance,\n\n```python\nfrom quart_auth import AuthUser, login_user, logout_user\n\n@app.route(\"/login\")\nasync def login():\n    # Check Credentials here, e.g. username & password.\n    ...\n    # We'll assume the user has an identifying ID equal to 2\n    login_user(AuthUser(2))\n    ...\n\n@app.route(\"/logout\")\nasync def logout():\n    logout_user()\n    ...\n```\n\nThe user (authenticated or not) is available via the global\n`current_user` including within templates,\n\n```python\nfrom quart import render_template_string\nfrom quart_auth import current_user\n\n@app.route(\"/\")\nasync def user():\n    return await render_template_string(\"{{ current_user.is_authenticated }}\")\n```\n\n## Contributing\n\nQuart-Auth is developed on [GitHub](https://github.com/pgjones/quart-auth). You are very welcome to\nopen [issues](https://github.com/pgjones/quart-auth/issues) or\npropose [pull requests](https://github.com/pgjones/quart-auth/pulls).\n\n### Testing\n\nThe best way to test Quart-Auth is with Tox,\n\n```console\n$ pip install tox\n$ tox\n```\n\nthis will check the code style and run the tests.\n\n## Help\n\nThe Quart-Auth [documentation](https://quart-auth.readthedocs.io) is the best places to\nstart, after that try searching [stack overflow](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/quart) or ask for help\n[on gitter](https://gitter.im/python-quart/lobby). If you still\ncan't find an answer please [open an issue](https://github.com/pgjones/quart-auth/issues).\n"], "modules": [{"name": "quart_auth", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "quart_auth.Action", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.extension.Action", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.authenticated_client", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.globals.authenticated_client", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.AuthUser", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.extension.AuthUser", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.basic_auth_required", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.basic_auth.basic_auth_required", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.current_user", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.globals.current_user", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.generate_auth_token", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.globals.generate_auth_token", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.login_required", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.globals.login_required", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.login_user", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.globals.login_user", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.logout_user", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.globals.logout_user", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.QuartAuth", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.extension.QuartAuth", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.renew_login", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.globals.renew_login", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.Unauthorized", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.extension.Unauthorized", "project": null}}, {"name": "quart_auth.UnauthorizedBasicAuth", "xref": {"fqname": "quart_auth.basic_auth.UnauthorizedBasicAuth", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "quart_auth.extension", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "quart_auth.extension._get_config_or_default", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "config_key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "app", "type": {"name": "Quart", "xref": {"fqname": "quart.Quart", "project": "quart"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "quart_auth.extension.DEFAULTS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "quart_auth.extension.Unauthorized", "bases": ["WerkzeugUnauthorized"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "quart_auth.extension.Action", "bases": ["Enum"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "quart_auth.extension.Action.DELETE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "quart_auth.extension.Action.PASS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "quart_auth.extension.Action.WRITE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "quart_auth.extension.Action.WRITE_PERMANENT", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "quart_auth.extension._AuthSerializer", "bases": ["URLSafeTimedSerializer"], "methods": [{"name": "quart_auth.extension._AuthSerializer.__in